.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-GRAPH-CHANNEL-AGE-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-graph-channel-age-stats \- FEAT-2184 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-graph-channel-age-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2184).
.PP
Reports min, max, and average channel age in seconds based on last_update timestamps from the gossip graph.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
